``last``
, 
``first``
, 
``select``
, 
``length``
 (#17415)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17405] refactored cli lexopt (#17405)
@app/dependabot:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17443] bumped shadow-rs from 1.6.0 to 1.7.0 (#17443)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17442] bumped sysinfo from 0.37.2 to 0.38.0 (#17442)
