``canonicalize``
 with 
``absolute``
 (#17412)
@pyz4:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17436] added join on advanced column expressions to polars (#17436)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17435] added 
``nulls-equal``
 argument to 
``polars join``
 (#17435)
@WindSoilder:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17426] updated assert_cmd to 2.1.1 (#17426)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17397] added support for 
``try {} finally {}``
 (#17397)
@sgvictorino:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17417] updated eml-parser to 0.1.5 (#17417)
@benblank:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17386] added a 
``umask``
 command (#17386)
@astral-l:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17332] fixed std repeat returning empty list on null input (#17332)
@ysthakur:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17330] allowed custom/external completers to override display value (#17330)
@KaiSforza:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17323] added 
``Type::Any``
 to input type for error_make (#17323)
